#: ../build/doc/usermanual/po/darktable-usermanual_profiled.xml:6126(para)
msgid ""
"Clicking on a combobox will open a list of available options. Click on the "
"item you want to select. Sometimes the selection list opens close to the "
"bottom or top of the screen and only part of the items are visible; scroll "
"with your mouse wheel to bring up the full list. Alternatively, you can also "
"use the mouse wheel and keyboard arrow keys to select an option."
