"color profile</quote> in the <emphasis>processing</emphasis> section of the "
"preferences dialog (see <xref linkend=\"processing\"/>) defines which method "
"is used. Note, however, that if the given ICC is LUT-based, or contains both "
"a LUT and a matrix, darktable will use LittleCMS 2 to render the colors "
"regardless of that configuration parameter's value."
