#: ../build/doc/usermanual/po/darktable-usermanual_profiled.xml:17869(para)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the module, you'll see Display Exposure Mask and to the "
"right of that, an icon <inlinegraphic fileref=\"images/"
"darkroom_module_icon_mask.png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"2%\" align=\"center\"/"
">. <emphasis>Click</emphasis> on this icon to see the mask which the Tone "
