#~ "during interactive work, it is therefore important that your GPU is "
#~ "allocated to do the more demanding center image (full) pixelpipe, while "
#~ "the smaller preview image can be processed in parallel by the CPU. Older "
#~ "versions of darktable would therefore not allow the preview pixelpipe to "
#~ "grab any OpenCL device."
#~ msgstr ""
